  "body": "### Description\n\nCurrently the Vertx MysqlPool allows settings the connection timeout, authentication plugin and possibly other properties. I didn't see any way to set it using the Quarkus Reactive Mysql extension. So currently we use a customized cloned extension which allows setting the properties mentioned above.\r\nThe authentication plugin is quite important as it allows connecting to AWS RDS databases using IAM token authentication. I can submit a PR if it's of interest.\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\n_No response_",
